title: Miami voters head to the polls as Democrats see chance to win mayoral race
description: Miami is holding its mayoral elections Tuesday, and for the first time in more than two decades, Democrats think they have a chance to win after President Trump endorsed the Republican in the race.
content: Miami is holding its mayoral elections Tuesday, and for the first time in more than two decades, Democrats think they have a chance to win after President Trump endorsed the Republican in the race.
